graph LR
    Kueue[Kueue Controller Manager]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Kueue -->|CRD mgmt<br/>pod orchestration| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>v1.25+<br/>REQUIRED]
    Kueue -->|TLS certificates<br/>webhook server| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>v1.17+<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional - Monitoring)
    Kueue -->|metrics exposure| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional - Job Types)
    Kueue -.->|TFJob/PyTorchJob<br/>MPIJob management| KubeflowOperator[Kubeflow Training Operator<br/>v1.9+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    Kueue -.->|RayJob/RayCluster<br/>management| RayOperator[Ray Operator<br/>v1.3+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    Kueue -.->|JobSet management| JobSetOperator[JobSet Operator<br/>v0.8+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    Kueue -.->|AppWrapper<br/>gang scheduling| AppWrapperOperator[AppWrapper Operator<br/>v1.1+<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional - Autoscaling)
    Kueue -.->|ProvisioningRequest<br/>node provisioning| ClusterAutoscaler[Cluster Autoscaler<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional - MultiKueue)
    Kueue -.->|multi-cluster<br/>job dispatch| RemoteCluster[Remote K8s Clusters<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% External Services
    Kueue -->|watch/patch<br/>workloads| K8sAPI
    Kueue -->|create<br/>Certificate CR| CertManager

    %% Integration Points (via K8s API)
    Jobs[Batch Jobs] -->|intercepted by| Kueue
    KubeflowJobs[Kubeflow Jobs<br/>TFJob/PyTorchJob] -.->|intercepted by| Kueue
    RayJobs[Ray Jobs<br/>RayJob/RayCluster] -.->|intercepted by| Kueue
    JobSetJobs[JobSet Resources] -.->|intercepted by| Kueue
    AppWrapperJobs[AppWrapper Resources] -.->|intercepted by| Kueue

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    %% NOTE: Kueue has NO internal ODH dependencies
    %% It's a standalone component

    %% Styling
    style Kueue fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% Required external
    style K8sAPI fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style CertManager fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    %% Optional external
    style Prometheus fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style KubeflowOperator fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style RayOperator fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style JobSetOperator fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style AppWrapperOperator fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style ClusterAutoscaler fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style RemoteCluster fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Managed resources
    style Jobs fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style KubeflowJobs fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style RayJobs fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style JobSetJobs fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style AppWrapperJobs fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
